Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:59.82,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}藍色的玻璃碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:05.70,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}遮去耀眼的烈日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:17.75,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}拖著空箱流浪四方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:26.14,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始終尋找心的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:32.52,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}待掌中接獲那份沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:38.06,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}又備下寬敞的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:51.08,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}將堅定的心就此珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:13.64,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}未來帶有怎樣的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:19.61,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}還是保持未知為好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:25.19,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在難以入眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:36.62,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}封印在抽屜的最深處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:42.71,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}光明 陰影 淚水 聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:51.89,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}都令我怦然心動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:57.06,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始終探尋注定的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:03.32,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}難得抓住一線希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:13.95,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}下一個注定又在遠方招手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:22.92,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如此終而復始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:43.23,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}尚未紮穩根基之時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:48.78,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}豈可掐去希望之花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.74,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}總有些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:55.87,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}分毫也無法動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:11:03.75,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}而那正是心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:08.76,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始終尋找心的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:14.85,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}待掌中接獲那份沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:20.52,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}又備下寬敞的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:34.62,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}將堅定的心就此珍藏
