Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:36.15,next_title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad2\fad(300,0)\pos(1112,600)}「畢業」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙上校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜破壞RA221基地作戰成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能還以烏魯伽魯一點顏色了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 今後的作戰也有點希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的戰鬥現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一直小看我們的烏魯伽魯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本次戰鬥之後 肯定會有大動作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要準備應對烏魯伽魯的反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也已經確認敵人有所行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天音副官 這裡輪不到你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣一來 MJP的駕駛員培養也上軌道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能培養出許多像他們一樣優秀的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利也就有望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要推進增產ASHMB
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 那戰鬥真的很艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責整備的可辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的Rhinos是你們的ASHMB的原型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你們也能打得那麼漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該能打得更漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要更好地掌握自己的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的機體裡是植入了DNA的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你駕駛它 操作就會是相對簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不要只依賴機械的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單方面的依賴關係是不會持久的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 找我什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想要新的色情影片 我手頭可沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們接到了再度返回學園的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來跟你說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 肯定又會在別的地方碰面的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 敵人似乎也已經開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是上次戰鬥的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儲存在Rhinos裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也承擔為下一代取得戰鬥數據的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之後會回到最前線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儲存在Rhinos裡的數據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是前輩還是我們 都是類似數據一樣的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doberman接下來會去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是回到最前線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會再見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你們怎麼在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我們也不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子 關鍵的地方少根筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是遺憾五人組
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的攻擊能成功 也是多虧了前輩們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你們可別在戰鬥中把我們的名聲都敗光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感覺很寬慰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬慰個啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這麼努力 結果受到這種對待？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴風教官叫你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾小隊的前輩們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾…小隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那是故意的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是真的誤會了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業…指的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 你們將結束培養期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式配屬到GDF軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說只有你們幾個跳級畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也將調離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去擔任戈迪利昂的艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們的長官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 去整理你們宿舍內的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天回到玫瑰之星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備接受下一個任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白沒
Comment: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#插曲#
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就讓我們畢業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「今後會毫無顧忌地把你們丟上戰場！」的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點落寞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛來這裡的時候 我都沒想過以後會有這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當時感覺就是被人不管三七二十一扔進這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你們分到同一個小隊的時候 感覺可震驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 下一個小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木俊一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駿河中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日立出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釘宮惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入江環
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都比我小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不懂的 儘管問我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來 駿河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始你基本不怎麼說話的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我都不知道該說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的記憶都被消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了上課和天氣之外也沒什麼可說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到這上課啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbits小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的攻擊力和機動力都很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是協調性 集中力和動作穩定性都是E
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是協調性 是E-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是說她的罩杯 那是差不多這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆是F就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,評分最差就是E了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼 從那之後就能開口聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我能拿走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是之前住在這間宿舍的學生的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那麼殘破了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我看的第一部漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這下爽快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不用再回來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們率先駕駛最新銳的ASHMB並且畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任誰都不會想到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做夢都想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想一個人躲起來哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想最後再畫張素描
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\pos(566,298)\fs72\frz44.633\c&H7EADC8&}遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 完全擺脫不了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒要問你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來整理書桌裡的東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(499,184)\frz13.64}交到絕佳{\c&H6772EC&}女友{\c&HFFFFFF&}的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是給男生看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\frz10.11\pos(453,227)\c&H2A1A0B&\3c&H82A5EF&}躍動的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…上課時候都在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格說別人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪我們被人說是遺憾五人組
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木說想最後繞校園一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒說！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的ASHMB現在正運來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天音大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白戶中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛開完會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地的經濟組織都吵著要ASHMB的技術和機體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們之前一直被對手摁著打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是頭一次取得勝利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASHMB和MJP機關引起注目也是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他們對ASHMB如此眼紅 並不是為了和敵人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是想自己國家爬到頂端而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和敵人戰鬥很不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過地球上的政治手腕也叫人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看他們對技術的渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的想資助格蘭賽列都市學園
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有的想讓駕駛員入學就讀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些不歸你管的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為西蒙司令目前不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去學園了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 已經收拾好了行李
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天應該就能出發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得 讓他們正式成為軍隊一員還有點早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還不能完全熟練地駕駛ASHMB
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且對茱莉亞系統也有點困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入江環和駿河中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於天生性格的緣故 比較適應系統
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 麻木和釘宮這兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了前線就會發怵 不能發揮實力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日立出雖然時不時能展現出爆發性的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不夠穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們在這裡已經學不到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱茱莉亞系統的方法 也只有在實戰中才能學到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在生死懸於一線的情況下才能學到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做明天的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASHMB？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 實物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟練習機體完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非得進行模擬演習？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得很早嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個模擬演習而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要這麼緊張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為是模擬演習才緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能比戰鬥還嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的要做這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我昨天說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue1和Red5表演對接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gold4在標準重力下射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為使用的是實體彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要注意測算重力 風向 濕度和大氣密度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Purple2負責指揮 Rose3從上空進行支援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演習就是這個形式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演我不擅長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之前你在全宇宙面前失敗了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就好了 有個表現機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就開開炮啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個地方指揮？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是表演用高臺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概這是最丟臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 Rabbits小隊將進行模擬演習
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到畢業前還有這種任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是擺脫遺憾五人組這個稱號的好機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 是不是想一口氣成為學園的英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個很棒的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得我們別失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue1 Gold4 Red5 升空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue1 Red5 對接
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rose3 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環 你飛得比計畫中要低啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gold4 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒人看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們給誰鼓掌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演習到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前很多地方對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不在了 會挺寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們很快也會上前線的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦 以後再會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾五人組
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業生 入場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頒發軍階章
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入江環
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釘宮惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木俊一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:19:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都在幹什麼啊 麻木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子的失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概你胃裡穿了三個洞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的風頭都被你搶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言那才不叫風頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點上來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會再回這兒了來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點…落寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後大家在哪裡 那裡就是我們的家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們五個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以遺憾小隊的身份努力吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小隊名字搞錯了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫「是嗎」！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜笨蛋蠢才呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:55.87,next_title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad2\pos(1030,600)}「慾望的大本營」
